# CONTRIBUTING

We love pull requests from everyone. By participating in this project, you agree our [code of conduct](./CODE_OF_CONDUCT).

## Getting Started

Here's a quick guide:

1. Fork the repo.
2. Create a new branch.
3. Make your changes.
4. Push to your branch.
5. Create a pull request.
6. Pat yourself on the back and wait for your pull request to be reviewed and merged.
7. Celebrate ðŸŽ‰
8. Repeat!
9. If you have any questions, feel free to ask.

## Styling Guide

Please use the recommended styling guide for this project. You can find it in the [biome.json](./biome.json) file on the formatter section.

## Tools

We use the following tools to maintain the project:

- [Biome](https://biomejs.dev) for formatting and linting.
- [pnpm](https://pnpm.io) for package management.
- [GitHub](https://github.com) for VCS hosting.

